[section#class.protected
    [:en] Protected member access
    [:zh_CN] 访问受保护成员

[%[:en] access control[![`protected]]
  [:zh_CN] 访问控制[![`protected]] ]
]

[para]
[:en] An additional access check beyond those described earlier in [#class.access] is
applied when a non-static data member or non-static member function is a
protected member of its designating class ([#class.access.base]) and is not
designated by a [~splice-expression].[#:fn]
[:zh_CN] 除 [#class.access] 中前文所述的访问检查之外，当某个非静态数据成员或非静态成员
函数是其指名类的受保护成员（[#class.access.base]）且并非由[~拼接表达式]所指名时，
还要实施另一种访问检查[#:fn]。

[note:foot]
[:en] This additional check does not apply to other members, e.g.,
static data members or enumerator member constants.
[:zh_CN] 这项额外检查并不适用于其它成员，比如静态数据成员或枚举符成员常量。
[note:end]

[:en] As described earlier, access to a protected member is granted because the
reference occurs in a friend or direct member of some class [`C].
[:zh_CN] 如前文所述，某个类 [`C] 授予对受保护成员的访问，是因为所进行的涉指发生于其友元或
直接成员之中。

[:en] If the access is to form a pointer to member ([#expr.unary.op]), the
[~nested-name-specifier] shall designate [`C] or a class derived from [`C].
[:zh_CN] 若这种访问是用于构成成员指针（[#expr.unary.op]），则其[~嵌套名说明符]应当代表
[`C] 或某个派生自 [`C] 的类。

[:en] Otherwise, if the access involves a (possibly implicit) object expression
([#expr.prim.id.general], [#expr.ref]), the class of the object expression
shall be [`C] or a class derived from [`C].
[:zh_CN] 否则，如果访问涉及某个（可能隐含的）对象表达式（[#expr.prim.id.general]，[#expr.ref]），
那么对象表达式的类应当为 [`C] 或某个派生自 [`C] 的类。

[begin:example]
[codeblock]
class B {
protected:
  int i;
  static int j;
};

class D1 : public B {
};

class D2 : public B {
  friend void fr(B*,D1*,D2*);
  void mem(B*,D1*);
};

void fr(B* pb, D1* p1, D2* p2) {
  pb->i = 1;                    // [:en] error [:zh_CN] 错误
  p1->i = 2;                    // [:en] error [:zh_CN] 错误
  p2->i = 3;                    // [:en] OK (access through a [`D2]) [:zh_CN] OK（通过 [`D2] 进行访问）
  p2->B::i = 4;                 // [:en] OK (access through a [`D2], even though designating class is [`B]) \
                                [:zh_CN] OK（通过 [`D2] 进行访问，虽然其指名类是 [`B]）
  int B::* pmi_B = &B::i;       // [:en] error [:zh_CN] 错误
  int B::* pmi_B2 = &D2::i;     // [:en] OK (type of [`&D2::i] is [`int B::*]) [:zh_CN] OK（[`&D2::i] 的类型为 [`int B::*]）
  B::j = 5;                     // [:en] error: not a friend of designating class [`B] [:zh_CN] 错误：并非指名类 [`B] 的友元
  D2::j = 6;                    // [:en] OK (because refers to static member) [:zh_CN] OK（因为指代了静态成员）
}

void D2::mem(B* pb, D1* p1) {
  pb->i = 1;                    // [:en] error [:zh_CN] 错误
  p1->i = 2;                    // [:en] error [:zh_CN] 错误
  i = 3;                        // [:en] OK (access through [`:key this]) [:zh_CN] OK（通过 [`:key this] 进行访问）
  B::i = 4;                     // [:en] OK (access through [`:key this], qualification ignored) \
                                [:zh_CN] OK（通过 [`:key this] 进行访问，忽略限定）
  int B::* pmi_B = &B::i;       // [:en] error [:zh_CN] 错误
  int B::* pmi_B2 = &D2::i;     // OK
  j = 5;                        // [:en] OK (because [`j] refers to static member) [:zh_CN] OK（因为 [`j] 指代了静态成员）
  B::j = 6;                     // [:en] OK (because [`B::j] refers to static member) [:zh_CN] OK（因为 [`B::j] 指代了静态成员）
}

void g(B* pb, D1* p1, D2* p2) {
  pb->i = 1;                    // [:en] error [:zh_CN] 错误
  p1->i = 2;                    // [:en] error [:zh_CN] 错误
  p2->i = 3;                    // [:en] error [:zh_CN] 错误
}
[codeblock:end]
[end:example]
